Text.SourceString: Goomgoom, hooman, it me, <NPCName>Gong</>!
GOOMGOOOOOM!!!//<NPCName>Gong</> scream in cavern! Remember?!
I remember all things in cavern! I remember Hooman. I remember earthshake.
Just kidding. I forget. <NPCName>Gong</> remember nothing.
Very happy <NPCName>Gong</> can be in village again! I can feel water, water everywhere!//Water here, water there, water in the air, so many water!
Hmm, <NPCName>Gong</> miss rain. When is rain, hooman? <NPCName>Gong</> want rain right now, <NPCName>Gong</> miss rain...
Rain rain rain rain rain~//GOOMGOOOOOOOM!!!
RAIN!!! GOOOOM!!!
RAIN!!! GOOOOM!!!
<NPCName>Gong</> is home forever now.//Thank Hooman.
Hmmmm, <NPCName>Gong</> look at you and <NPCName>Gong</> hungry.
<NPCName>Gong</> speak Giant. <NPCName>Gong</> speak Fish. <NPCName>Gong</> speak Hooman.
Fish? Okay. Wait wait...//<NPCName>Gong</> need to focus. I know this.//Blub...blub blub... See?
<NPCName>Gong</> has so much to do today! Busy, busy!
Island is thirsty. <NPCName>Gong</> will ask for rain!
<NPCName>Groo</> like to run around forest.//<NPCName>Groo</> is so fun! So goomgoom!
I love <NPCName>Groo</>.
Rain is best! Earth is best! Wind is best! Fire is best!//Everything is best! Goom!
So many things for <NPCName>Gong</> to do today! What do?!
Busy busy so busy!
<NPCName>Grog</> so slow. But sometimes slow is nice.
<NPCName>Grog</> is nice.//I love <NPCName>Grog</>.
<NPCName>Gong</> ask <NPCName>Grog</> to run today, but  <NPCName>Grog</> no wanna...
Ice Season is nice. Is cold out.//Water everywhere!
But forest have no yummy food in Ice Season.*sigh*
Hmm, Ice Season! Time to play in river!
Hmm, Falling Season! What do, what do...
<NPCName>Grog</> want to go to Hooman village. So fun! So goomgoom!//<NPCName>Gong</> wanna go too.
Hooman Village have Hooman food. Many spikey fruits.//Ice cold food. Tasty waters! Yummy yummy.
Enjoy rain, Hooman!
There is Hooman that throw flower in lake. Why?//<NPCName>Gong</> have to clean it...
Tiny Hooman lost ball in river. It deep below now.//Even <NPCName>Gong</> cannot get.
Many new sprouts this season.//Giants need to speak to Goddess and gift fruits.//Giants love Goddess.
River and lake are full of fish now!//Water is alive again. Sprouting Season is best.
<NPCName>Grog</> have many forest friends. I always see <NPCName>Grog</> play with them.//I want to play with them too.

Forest friends say we can play on fifth week of Ice Season. But we need ice! No play if no ice.//Sad 'cause so far, fifth week of Ice Season have no ice so forest friends can not play. Maybe next Ice Season.
<NPCName>Grog</> sad the leaves are falling...but is okay Hooman.//Water will make them alright again.
Forest will be green again after drinking ice water soon. Be not sad.//I will try to make it all okay again so <NPCName>Grog</> can be happy.
Snow snow snow! <NPCName>Gong</> wanna make snowpeople like in Hooman Village.
<NPCName>Gong</> asked <NPCName>Chieftain</> to play in snow but <NPCName>Chieftain</> no wanna.
Hooman need help with tools? <NPCName>Gong</> can help! Go to center of village.//Check the temple.
<NPCName>Gort</> lied and stoned us all many moons ago.//<NPCName>Gong</> get sad when remember. But <NPCName>Gong</> still love <NPCName>Gort</>.
<NPCName>Gort</> is angry all the time inside.//I hope <NPCName>Gort</> happy one day. Heart feel like river.
Are you here with fruits, Hooman? No fruits no help.
Heh heh heh! Goombozled! Just kidding.
<NPCName>Gong</> likes being home. <NPCName>Gong</> can listen to the water trickle.//Very nice and calming. Goom~
